Tool generates a randomly colored image of given size. Arguments control which channels are random and which non-random channels are "black" or "white".

Comments in source file may be inaccurate.

To build:
	make

To build for debugging:
	make DEBUG=1

Usage:
	./badpng outfile.png x y randmask blackmask

